title: Welcome To 25 Whistles!
itunes:title: Welcome To 25 Whistles!
description:
25 Whistles is a weekly 25-episode timely limited series focused strictly on college and NFL football. Host Bobby Bones brings on his sports obsessed friends: Adam Hambrick (singer-songwriter / musician) and Kickoff Kevin (segment producer and on-air news reporter), Producer Eddie and Head Producer Mike D.  It will be a podcast unlike any other show...but just like all the rest!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
